      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs darrija ta/ un\nbeitse to Neddetu ar to/ tad de-\nwe wiꞥſch tam Raëli/ ſawu Mei-\ntu par Seewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lahbang dewe Raëlei/\nsawu Kalponi Bila/ par Kalponi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs gahje arri-\ndsan pee Raëles/ un miḣleja to\nRaëli wairak ne ka Leii/ un tas\nKalpoja pee winna wehl zittus\nfeptin Gaddus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS redseja/\nka Lea eenihdeta tappe/ tad dar-\nrija wiꞥſch to augligu/ bet Raë-\nle bija neaugliga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lea tappe gruhta/ un\ndsemdeja Dehtu/ un noẜauze win-\nna Wahrdtu Rubbens/ jo ta faz-\nzija: Tapehz/ ka tas KUNGS\nmannas Behdas irr skattijis/ jo\nnu mihtohs mann mans Wihrs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta tappe atkaṫ gruh-\nta/ un dsemdeja Dehtu/ un faz-\nzija: Tapehz/ ka tas KUNGS\ndsirdejis/ man eenihdetu effam/\nirr winch man arridsan to de-\nwis/ un noẜauze winna Wahrdtu\nSihmeans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta tappe atkaṫ gruh-\nta/ un dsemdeja Dehtu/ un faz-\nzija: Nu/ ſcho Brihdi mans\nWihrs matt peedsihwohs/ jo es\nefinu winnam trihs Dehtus dsem-\ndejsi/ tadeht noẜauze ta winna\nWahrdtu Lewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna tappe atkaṫ\ngruhta/ un dsemdeja Dehtu/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "arridsan par to Kalposchanu/ jo fazziia : Scho Brihdi flawefcht\nes to KUNGU/ tadeht noẜauz-\nta winna Wahrdtu Juhda/ un\nta mittejahs dseindeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXX. Nodalla.\nRaëleirr ne-augliga : 1. Un dohd ſawu Kalp-\nni Bilu Jehkabam par Seewu : 3.\ndsemde Danu un Nawtalu : 5/7. Lea doh-\narri ſawu Kalponi Silpu Jehkabam par Se-\nwu/ ta dsemde Gadu/ Ahseru : 9. DDeiw-\npadarra Kaëlu augligu / ta dsemde Jahsep-\n22. Jehkabs ſaderr ar Lahbanu tahs Ka-\nposchanas pehz : 25.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad nu Raële redseja/\nta Jehkabam ne dsemde-\nja/ eenihdeja ta ſaw-\nMahsu/ un fazziia us Jehkabu-\nDabbu man Behrnus/ bet ja ne-\ntad inan ja-mirſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad apskaitahs Jehkab-\nus Raëles/ un fazziia : Woj-\npar Deeiu efmu/ kas tew tawa-\nMeefas Angtue leedsis irr?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta fazziia : Reds/ ſche i-\nmanna Kalpone Bila/eij pee tah-\nka ta us mann Klehpi dsemde-\nun es arridsan zaur winnu a-\nbehrnota tohpu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna dewe tam Bi-\nfawu Kalponi par Seewu / u-\nJehkabs gabje pee tahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Bila tappe gruhta/ u-\ndsemdeja Jehkabam Dehtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazziia Raële : Dee-\nirr man teesajis / un arrids-\nmannu Balsi paklaustjis /\nman Dehtu dewis / tadeht n-\nfauze ta winna Wahrdtu Dan-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Bila Raëles Kalpo-\ntappe atkaṫ gruhta/ un dsemde-\nJehkabam to ohtru Dehtu.\n"
    }
  ],
